Text: Beta BrunchBeta reunion weekend would be complete without the Beta Brunch at the Bensons We will be serving Sunday Morning from AM until we kick the last Beta out of the house The menu is still being prepared but rest assured that there will be some good Zodiac vodka around the house for Bloody Marys Screwdrivers Martinis Jello Shots or whatever i t takes to erase the pain from three days of partying Below is a photo of CDi enjoying some of that Benson Beta Brunch hospitality Shoot me an email and let me know asap if you will be hanging around for the brunch Directions to follow Tom
